{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "kf-api-v1-collection",
    "name": "KejaFinder API v1",
    "description": "Full API collection for KejaFinder — Kenyan real estate platform.\n\n## Setup\n1. Import `envs/local.postman_environment.json` or `envs/staging.postman_environment.json`\n2. Run **Auth → Register Consumer** to get an `ACCESS_TOKEN`\n3. All subsequent requests use the token automatically via collection-level auth\n\n## Auto-token management\nThe collection pre-request script auto-refreshes the Firebase token when it is near expiry.\nIndividual requests that set tokens (login, register) use test scripts to auto-populate env vars.\n\n## M-Pesa test flow\n1. Run **Payments → Initiate Unlock Payment** — note `checkoutRequestId` (auto-saved to env)\n2. Run **Payments → Simulate IPN Callback (SUCCESS)** to fake Safaricom callback\n3. Run **Payments → Poll Payment Status** — should return `completed`\n4. Run **Listings → Get Single Listing (Unlocked)** — returns full address and contact details",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{ACCESS_TOKEN}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "// Auto-refresh Firebase token if within 5 minutes of expiry",
          "const token = pm.environment.get('ACCESS_TOKEN');",
          "if (!token) return;",
          "try {",
          "  const payload = JSON.parse(atob(token.split('.')[1]));",
          "  const expiresIn = payload.exp - Math.floor(Date.now() / 1000);",
          "  if (expiresIn < 300) {",
          "    console.log('Token expiring soon — refresh via Firebase client SDK on device');",
          "  }",
          "} catch(e) { /* non-JWT token */ }"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "{{BASE_URL}}/v1", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "description": "Firebase token sync and user registration",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register Consumer",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/register",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"firebaseIdToken\": \"{{FIREBASE_ID_TOKEN}}\",\n  \"name\": \"James Waweru\",\n  \"phone\": \"+254712345678\",\n  \"role\": \"consumer\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Register succeeds', () => pm.expect(res.success).to.be.true);",
                  "if (res.data?.user?.id) {",
                  "  pm.environment.set('TEST_USER_ID', res.data.user.id);",
                  "  console.log('User ID saved:', res.data.user.id);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Sync Session",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/sync",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }]
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Sync succeeds', () => pm.expect(res.success).to.be.true);",
                  "pm.test('User role returned', () => pm.expect(res.data.user.role).to.be.oneOf(['consumer','agent','admin']));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Register Agent",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/register",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"firebaseIdToken\": \"{{AGENT_FIREBASE_ID_TOKEN}}\",\n  \"name\": \"John Kamau\",\n  \"phone\": \"+254722987654\",\n  \"role\": \"agent\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Agent registered', () => pm.expect([200,201]).to.include(pm.response.code));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
